.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568990/extras/ed1c5021ee7228765509299866e5a9a0.webm?t=1739332088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2568990/extras/ed1c5021ee7228765509299866e5a9a0.mp4?t=1739332088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>CoA is currently in early access and created by a solo developer (me!). I am actively seeking feedback to improve the game. Stay tuned for upcoming additions including more missions, enemy variety, maps, game modes, and an expanded arsenal of weapons and armor. Your input is invaluable in shaping the future of CoA!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Champion of Andia is currently designed for Windows only. It is not compatible with Mac or other operating systems.</i></p>",
